Reasoning: The paper is about multimodal language analysis, which involves modeling language from text, visual, and acoustic modalities. This falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also uses BERT, a popular language model, and fine-tunes it for multimodal analysis, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
